View AEME variables

view_aeme_vars.Rd

View AEME variables

Usage

view_aeme_vars(group = "all")

Arguments

group

character string to filter variables by group. Default is "all". Options include "HYD" (hydrodynamic), "LKE" (Lake), "RAD" (Radiation), "CHM" (Chemistry), "PHS" (Phosphorus), "NIT" (Nitrogen), "CAR" (Carbon), "SIL" (Silica), "MET" (Meteorologica), "ZOO" (Zooplankton), "PHY" (Phytoplankton),

Value

A data frame with AEME variables
